"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The Trump administration is increasing pressure on Cuba's communist government. This is part of their ongoing campaign against Cuba.\",            \"english_title\": \"Trump Increases Pressure on Cuba\",            \"translated_version\": \"El gobierno de Trump est\u00e1 poniendo m\u00e1s presi\u00f3n en el gobierno comunista de Cuba. Esto es parte de su campa\u00f1a contra Cuba.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Trump pone presi\u00f3n en Cuba\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Russia and China are showing unity on the world stage, but there are limits to their cooperation, according to the BBC's Russia Editor.\",            \"english_title\": \"Russia and China Show Unity\",            \"translated_version\": \"Rusia y China muestran unidad en el mundo, pero hay l\u00edmites a su cooperaci\u00f3n, seg\u00fan el editor de Rusia de la BBC.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Rusia y China unidos\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"There are concerns about Russian espionage in Austria after a spy scandal. This has brought back fears of Austria being a center for Russian spying activities.\",            \"english_title\": \"Russian Espionage Concerns in Austria\",            \"translated_version\": \"Hay preocupaciones sobre espionaje ruso en Austria despu\u00e9s de un esc\u00e1ndalo de esp\u00edas. Esto ha tra\u00eddo de vuelta miedos de que Austria sea un centro de actividades de espionaje ruso.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Preocupaci\u00f3n por esp\u00edas rusos en Austria\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"France and Italy criticized a video of Itamar Ben-Gvir mocking activists detained at an Israeli port. This has caused international concern.\",            \"english_title\": \"France and Italy Criticize Video\",            \"translated_version\": \"Francia e Italia criticaron un video de Itamar Ben-Gvir burl\u00e1ndose de activistas detenidos en un puerto israel\u00ed. Esto ha causado preocupaci\u00f3n internacional.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Francia e Italia critican video\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The World Health Organization reported 139 suspected deaths and 600 cases in its latest update. This is part of their ongoing health monitoring.\",            \"english_title\": \"WHO Reports Suspected Deaths\",            \"translated_version\": \"La Organizaci\u00f3n Mundial de la Salud report\u00f3 139 muertes sospechosas y 600 casos en su \u00faltima actualizaci\u00f3n. Esto es parte de su monitoreo de salud.\",            \"translated_title\": \"OMS reporta muertes sospechosas\"        }    ]}"